<h4>Practical Tips..., Powerful tools..., Immediate Results!</h4>
<h3>Parents will learn how to:</h3>
<ul class="list_004">
<li>Handle Misbehavior Without Breaking a Sweat</li>
<li>Neutralize Arguments&hellip;.Every time</li>
<li>Teach Kids to Listen&hellip;the First Time</li>
<li>Avoid Power Struggles</li>
<li>Manage Whining and Complaining</li>
<li>Know What to do When Your Kids Leave You Speechless</li>
<li>Build Cooperation with School People</li>
<li>Turn Your Words into Gold</li>
</ul>
<blockquote>You will walk away with 9 essential parenting skills that are guaranteed to work! Class includes a workbook, binder notebook, small group interaction, large group lecture, and DVD presentation with Dr. Charles Fay, Jim Fay, and Dr. Foster Cline.</blockquote>
